- Hello guys, this is my latest project that I have been working on, on and off for the last 6 months. The map is made with legit (scroll) bhop in mind (what every map should be). I went with a realistic style since it's what I prefer to do when I'm mapping. The difficulty of the map is just an old classic mp bhop that almost everyone can complete since it's easy and medium. There are also a lot of checkpoints, which gives the player a better experience. There is also 5-6 easter eggs in the map.

Remade version of bhop_focus. Gameplay were unstable so heres another one that isnt as compact.

**Improvements**

• Smoother gameplay for speedrunning on both bhop categories
• Better lightning such as HDR and fixed dark levels
• Teleporters being straight forward
• New look with better fitting concrete textures
• No bad contrast on bhop pads 
• Cool particle system to make it more alive
• Bonus longer and improved
• Player clips above checkpoints should be fixed not to interrupt gameplay
• Filesize increased from 101 mb to 62 mb

The old map were made for the sake of the wall idea, so i thought i could make a decent gameplay into it and it would be fine. This map fits better as a speedrun map but still kept to a difficulty standard with a few obstacles as levels increases.

Time estimate for avg player: 12-16 seconds.

My first ever map. . . I've been bhopping for 2 years now so I decided, "why not make a map for a thing I love to do so much?" :^) Hope you all enjoy, and feel free to use this map in your bhop server. Comment the IP for your server so I can try it out on your server =)

***NOTE: IF YOU WANT A BONUS, JUST PUT THE START OF THE BONUS AT THE END OF THE MAP AND THE END OF THE BONUS AT THE START OF THE TIME***

Bhop_FL
~~~~~~~
By Frozer Laxegon @ frozeraism.blogspot.com
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Description :
Bhop map with 5 levels, 4 sections for each level, includes a mini long jump.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Features :
~Big and wide spawn
~Mini long jump
~5 levels with 4 sections on each level
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Cvars :
sv_airaccelerate 1200
sv_enablebunnyhopping 1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Misc. Info :
Softwares used : Hammer Editor[Source SDK]
Mapping time : 1 hour 15 mins[10 mins for layout, 15 mins for ideas, 30 mins for adding challenges, 20 mins for final touchup]
Custom textures : None used
Skybox : militia_hdr
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
How To Install :
[1]Extract archive using Winrar
[2]Drag and put bhop_fl.bsp into ./Steam/steamapps/<yoursteamusername>/Counter-Strike:Source/cstrike/maps
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
